thread.title: BRIEF-Jean unit to issue new shares at T$18 per share for working capital replenishment

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Jean unit to issue new shares at T$18 per share for working capital replenishment

organizations.name: reuters) - jean co ltd * says co’s optoelectronics

text:
Feb 6(Reuters) - Jean Co Ltd
* Says co’s optoelectronics unit plans to issue 13 million to 20 million new shares for working capital replenishment, with par value of T$10 per share and issue price at T$18 per share
* 10 percent of the new shares to be offered to employees and 90 percent to be offered to the existing shareholders
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/AZTdw2
